org.xandercat.pmdb.util

Class DoubleStatistics

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.xandercat.pmdb.util.NumberStatistics<Double>
      • org.xandercat.pmdb.util.DoubleStatistics

  • public class DoubleStatistics
extends NumberStatistics<Double>
    Statistics for double values. This class expects the list of doubles to be non-null, contain no null values, and have a size of at least 1. Standard deviation and interquartile range are lazy calculated when needed.
    Author:
    Scott Arnold
